			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2">
				<div class="text">
					<p>
						But 6 billion do have mobile phones. We send illustrated children’s stories by text message and messaging apps to get families talking face-to-face. 
					</p>
					<p>
						Still, many parents never had an adult who talked with them, or they don’t know that talking’s important. Our stories use colored prompts to help them start and build conversation habits that can overcome poverty’s damage. 
					</p>
					<p>
						And it’s 300x cheaper than just shipping paperbacks. 
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			
		</section>

